OL,3,CBin workers attacked with weapons in
OL,4,Croad rage ambush
OL,6,FFootage has been released showing bin
OL,7,Fworkers being ambushed and attacked
OL,8,Fwith weapons following a road rage
OL,9,Fincident in Stoke-on-Trent.
OL,11,FJoe Corden, 29, Jack Spackman, 25,
OL,12,FKyle Worthington, 21 and a youth
OL,13,Flaunched the assaults on the council
OL,14,Fworkers and their lorries in Birches
OL,15,FHead.
