OL,3,CBin workers attacked with weapons in
OL,4,Croad rage ambush
OL,6,FCCTV footage was played at Stoke-on-
OL,7,FTrent Crown Court showing how the bin
OL,8,Fmen were attacked and weapons
OL,9,Fincluding a sledgehammer, axe, baton
OL,10,Fand pole were used. The court heard
OL,11,Fhow at one point a gun was also fired
OL,12,Fin the direction of the wagon.
OL,14,FIt happened 21 March 2023 after Corden
OL,15,Flost his temper following a near
OL,16,Fcollision between his Vauxhall Corsa
OL,17,Fand the bin wagon at the junction of
OL,18,FBirches Head Road and Fairhaven Road.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/14
