OL,3,CBin workers attacked with weapons in
OL,4,Croad rage ambush
OL,6,FIn court this week prosecutor Nick
OL,7,FTatlow said: "Both had to stop to
OL,8,Favoid a collision between their
OL,9,Fvehicles. Corden got out and went to
OL,10,Fthe driver's side of the bin wagon,
OL,11,Fclimbed on the step and punched the
OL,12,Fdriver three times to his face. The
OL,13,Fdriver and two colleagues got out the
OL,14,Fbin wagon and confronted the
OL,15,Fdefendant. There was a scuffle and the
OL,16,Fdefendant was twice knocked down.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
