OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F375A1738191513
OL,3,CBin workers attacked with weapons in
OL,4,Croad rage ambush
OL,6,F"They got back in the wagon and the
OL,7,Fdefendant tried to open the nearside
OL,8,Fdoor, plainly intent on further
OL,9,Fviolence. He threatened to kill one of
OL,10,Fthe colleagues and said he was going
OL,11,Fto fetch a knife and gun.
OL,13,F"The defendant went to his car and
OL,14,Fpicked up a lollypop pole. He ran to
OL,15,Fthe wagon and started to hit the
OL,16,Fdriver's side breaking the pole. The
OL,17,Fdriver started to drive off. The
OL,18,Fdefendant was still hitting the wagon
OL,19,Fwith the broken lollypop pole."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
