OL,3,CBin workers attacked with weapons in
OL,4,Croad rage ambush
OL,6,FThe lorry driver then returned to the
OL,7,Fcouncil depot, the court heard, where
OL,8,Fhe had pain to both sides of his jaw,
OL,9,Fa swollen nose and cuts inside and
OL,10,Foutside his mouth. The bin wagon was
OL,11,Fnot damaged.
OL,13,FShortly after the first attack, Corden
OL,14,Frecruited his friends and stopped his
OL,15,Fvehicle in from of another bin lorry
OL,16,Fin Birches Head Road.
OL,18,FIn court the prosecutor suggested
OL,19,FCorden mistook this bin wagon for the
OL,20,Fone involved in the earlier incident.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/14
