OL,6,FHe said: "Corden and Spackman ran to
OL,7,Fthe bin wagon, Corden with an axe,
OL,8,FSpackman with a sledgehammer. They
OL,9,Fwere closely followed by a youth with
OL,10,Fa metal bar and baton.
OL,12,F"Corden attacked the wagon windows
OL,13,Fwith the axe and the youth attacked a
OL,14,Fbin man. Corden smashed the windscreen
OL,15,Fwith the axe. The youth attacked a bin
OL,16,Fman, Corden joined in. Corden joined
OL,17,FSpackman who was attacking the
OL,18,Fdriver's side with a sledgehammer.
OL,19,FSpackman smashed the driver's door
OL,20,Fwindow and the small window behind it.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/14
