OL,3,CBin workers attacked with weapons in
OL,4,Croad rage ambush
OL,6,F"A bin man injured was assisted by
OL,7,Fmembers of the public. He was taken to
OL,8,Fhospital by ambulance. Two gashes to
OL,9,Fhis head were glued and he was given
OL,10,Fpaper stitches for a cut under his
OL,11,Fleft eye. He also had a gash to his
OL,12,Fupper thigh and a cut to his
OL,13,Fcollarbone."
OL,15,FThe court also heard the colleague had
OL,16,Fa deep laceration to his head which
OL,17,Fwas glued and bruising to his left arm
OL,18,Fand wrist and following the second
OL,19,Fattack, the damage to the wagon was
OL,20,F#3,794.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/14
