OL,4,Croad rage ambush
OL,6,FThe Vauxhall Corsa was later found by
OL,7,Fpolice in Kidsgrove, with the
OL,8,Fsledgehammer and Corden's hat inside
OL,9,Fit. The gun, a blank firing self
OL,10,Floading pistol, was seized from
OL,11,FWorthington's home on 5 April 2023.
OL,13,FWorthington told police in his
OL,14,Finterview that Corden had told him he
OL,15,Fhad been beaten up by some lads from
OL,16,FSneyd Green and he had gone to collect
OL,17,Fthe youth and Spackman. He said he
OL,18,Ffired a blank firing pistol towards
OL,19,Fthe bin wagon.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/14
