OL,11,FImpact statement from the bin workers
OL,12,Fwere heard in court.
OL,14,FOne said: "I had a gun pointed at me
OL,15,Fand fired. I have since struggled with
OL,16,Feveryday tasks. I suffer with
OL,17,Fflashbacks and nightmares and am
OL,18,Fconstantly looking over my shoulder. I
OL,19,Ffinished work due to ill health and
OL,20,Fhad worked for the council for 38
OL,21,Fyears."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/14
