OL,3,CBin workers attacked with weapons in
OL,4,Croad rage ambush
OL,6,FWorthington, of Abbey Road, Abbey
OL,7,FHulton, pleaded guilty conspiring to
OL,8,Fcause grievous bodily harm with intent
OL,9,Fand possessing a firearm with intent
OL,10,Fto cause fear of violence. He also
OL,11,Ffalls to be sentenced for other
OL,12,Funrelated matters including dangerous
OL,13,Fdriving.
OL,15,FThe case was adjourned until 7
OL,16,FFebruary when Spackman and Worthington
OL,17,Fare expected to be sentenced. Corden's
OL,18,Fbasis of plea has not been accepted by
OL,19,Fthe prosecution so his case could be
OL,20,Ffurther adjourned.
